TITLE: Requesting Notification Permissions with Notifee in React Native
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to request notification permissions from users and handle the response based on whether permission was granted or declined.
SOURCE: https://github.com/invertase/notifee/blob/main/docs/react-native/ios/permissions.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import notifee, { AuthorizationStatus } from '@notifee/react-native';

async function requestUserPermission() {
  const settings = await notifee.requestPermission();

  if (settings.authorizationStatus >= AuthorizationStatus.AUTHORIZED) {
    console.log('Permission settings:', settings);
  } else {
    console.log('User declined permissions');
  }
}
```

