TITLE: Creating Android Notification Channel with Notifee
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a notification channel with basic configuration including ID, name, lights, vibration and importance settings. This is essential for Android 8.0+ notifications.
SOURCE: https://github.com/invertase/notifee/blob/main/docs/react-native/android/channels.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_0

